&lt;div class=&quot;section page-centered&quot;&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;At Figma, one of our values is Grow as you go. We believe in hiring hard-working, curious people who are excited to learn and develop their skills. If you’re excited about this role but your past experience doesn’t align perfectly with the points outlined in the job description, we encourage you to apply anyways. You may be just the right candidate for this or other roles.&lt;/div&gt;
